text: "Baby, You're a Rich Man" is a 1967 song by The Beatles and was released as a B-side to All You Need Is Love. It went to number 1 in Australia and number 34 in the United States. It was an unfinished song by John Lennon. ==References== Category:The Beatles songs Category:1967 songs Category:Psychedelic rock songs Category:Psychedelic pop songs
title: Baby, You're a Rich Man
